      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * RubiChess</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Macrothylacia_rubi_male,_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Macrothylacia_rubi_male%2C_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg/330px-Macrothylacia_rubi_male%2C_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Macrothylacia_rubi_male%2C_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg/500px-Macrothylacia_rubi_male%2C_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Macrothylacia_rubi_male%2C_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg/960px-Macrothylacia_rubi_male%2C_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Macrothylacia_rubi_male,_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Macrothylacia rubi <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>RubiChess</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, licensed under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPL v3.0</a>.\nRubiChess started in 2017 as <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a> engine and soon evolved to a <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> engine first using <a href=\"/Rotated_Bitboards\" title=\"Rotated Bitboards\">rotated bitboards</a> and subsequently <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">magic bitboards</a> (about 24% faster) to determine <a href=\"/Sliding_Piece_Attacks\" title=\"Sliding Piece Attacks\">sliding piece attacks</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. In September 2020, Andreas Matthies announced RubiChess <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2018_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboard_Board-Definition#CBoardDef\" title=\"Bitboard Board-Definition\">Classical Bitboard Board-Definition</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards#Plain\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Plain Magic Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a> (1.3)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a> with <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning#ZugzwangVerification\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Verification</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ProbCut\" title=\"ProbCut\">ProbCut</a> (1.3)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#Extendedfutilitypruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Extended Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#MoveCountBasedPruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Late Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Reverse_Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Reverse Futility Pruning\">Reverse Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">SEE Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/PV-Move\" title=\"PV-Move\">PV-Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Captures\" title=\"Captures\">Captures</a> by <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV/LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic#CMHist\" title=\"History Heuristic\">Counter Moves History</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> (RubiChess NNUE) </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rook_on_Open_File\" title=\"Rook on Open File\">Rooks on (Semi) Open Files</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hanging_Piece\" title=\"Hanging Piece\">Hanging Pieces</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pin\" title=\"Pin\">Pinned Pieces</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn/King Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Duo_Trio_Quart_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Duo Trio Quart (Bitboards)\">Phalanx</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Candidate_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Candidate Passed Pawn\">Candidate Passed Pawn</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/King_Safety#Attacking\" title=\"King Safety\">Attacks</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety#PawnStorm\" title=\"King Safety\">Pawn Storm</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tempo#Tempo_Bonus\" title=\"Tempo\">Tempo Bonus</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018_...\">2018 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2018 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67594\">RubiChess 0.9 is out</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=68559\">RubiChess 1.1</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=69876\">RubiChess 1.3</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 11, 2019 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70878\">Rubichess 1.4</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 31, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69754&amp;start=369\">Re: New engine releases 2019</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 17, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=74828&amp;start=5\">Re: Orion 0.7&#160;: NNUE experiment</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 21, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75016\">RubiChess NNUE player implemented</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 06, 2020</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75016&amp;start=64\">Re: RubiChess NNUE player implemented</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 01, 2020</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76209&amp;start=225\">Re: New engine releases &amp; news 2021</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 14, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77157\">Rubichess NN questions</a> by <a href=\"/Jon_Dart\" title=\"Jon Dart\">Jon Dart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 23, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77503&amp;start=55\">Re: will Tcec allow Stockfish with a Leela net to play?</a> by <a href=\"/Connor_McMonigle\" title=\"Connor McMonigle\">Connor McMonigle</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=77665\">RubiChess 2.2</a> by Boban Stanojević, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 07, 2021</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/Matthies/RubiChess\">GitHub - Matthies/RubiChess: Another chess engine</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/Matthies/NN\">GitHub - Matthies/NN</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=RubiChess&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">RubiChess</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/40</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/rubi\">rubi - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rub%C3%AD\">Rubí from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rub%C3%AD_Rodr%C3%ADguez\">Rubí Rodríguez from Wikipedia</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Mathematician#RRodriguez\" title=\"Mathematician\">Rubí Rodríguez</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rub%C3%AD,_Barcelona\">Rubí, Barcelona from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruby\">Ruby from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruby_(disambiguation)\">Ruby (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruby_character\">Ruby character from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruby_(programming_language)\">Ruby (programming language) from Wikipedia</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ruby&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ruby (page does not exist)\">Ruby</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:The_Rolling_Stones\" title=\"Category:The Rolling Stones\">The Rolling Stones</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruby_Tuesday_(song)\">Ruby Tuesday</a>, Official 1991, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/fvp6gseKJS8?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RubiChess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macrothylacia_rubi\">Macrothylacia rubi</a>, male, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Macrothylacia_rubi_male,_veelvraat_mannetje.jpg\">Image</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Rasbak\">Rasbak</a>, May 11, 2011, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/Matthies/RubiChess/blob/master/ChangeLog.txt\">RubiChess/ChangeLog.txt at master · Matthies/RubiChess · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75016\">RubiChess NNUE player implemented</a> by <a href=\"/Andreas_Matthies\" title=\"Andreas Matthies\">Andreas Matthies</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 06, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/Matthies/RubiChess/blob/master/ChangeLog.txt\">RubiChess/ChangeLog.txt at master · Matthies/RubiChess · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228203734\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.634 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 112/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 230/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6153-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228203733 and revision id 25515\n -->\n"
